elfeckcom
===============================================================================
(*) Source for the http://elfeck.com website
(*) This might be very horrible Haskell and even worse Javascript

(*) Please do not use the images from /static/img/ without asking me first


credits
===============================================================================
(*) The backend is built with Spock: https://github.com/agrafix/Spock
(*) The code is heavily based on: https://github.com/agrafix/funblog
(*) Thanks to agrafix and the haskell irc


content format
===============================================================================
(*) Post Layout
    > Title
    > Categories
    > Content
    > Creation Time Stamp
    > Modify Time Stamp
    > Access level
    > Type

(*) Post Types
    0: Website Main Post
    1: Blog Post
    2: Twitter-like Snippet

(*) Submit Types (json)
    0: Inset
    1: Update
    2: Delete


MD to html parsing
===============================================================================
    > Headline		==
    > Headline		#, ##, ...
    > Html		<html>\n ... \n</html>
    > Linebreaks	double space \n
    > New paragraph	empty line
    > i	  		* *
    > b			** **
    > link		[name](url)
    > img		![name](url)